},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tbody",
"attrs":{
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-1 row-odd"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"a47732",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Dumping syndrome/postprandial hypoglycemia (tachycardia, sweating, abdominal pain, nausea, vomiting, diarrhea)"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"351ef2",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Rapid transit of undigested food into small intestines"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"8489d7",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Early symptoms (1 hour postprandial) caused by fluid shift into the GI tract (no hypoglycemia)"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"496344",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Late symptoms (2-3 hours postprandial), hypoglycemia caused by insulin surge in response to hyperglycemia"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"89222e",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Avoid foods high in simple sugar; replace with higher-fiber/high-protein foods"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"9cc2c3",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Avoid sweetened beverages (including alcohol)"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-2 row-even"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"da2a57",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Chronic loose stool"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"1a0d1b",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"May relate to rapid transit of food to small intestines, similar to dumping syndrome"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"967a07",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Consider small intestine bacterial overgrowth"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"43feae",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Adherence to dietary modifications to avoid dumping syndrome"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"acdadc",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Rifaximin if bacterial overgrowth is suspected"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-3 row-odd"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"f1ffe2",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Kidney stones"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"f0f3b3",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Increased urinary oxalic acid related to fat malabsorption"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"40fdfb",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Diet low in fat and oxalate, calcium supplementation, increased hydration"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-4 row-even"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"789f82",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Gallstones"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"7b068f",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Bile stasis, increased biliary cholesterol saturation with rapid weight loss"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"fb5f54",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Ultrasonography if symptomatic"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"71380b",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Cholecystectomy is definitive treatment"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"b67667",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Ursodeoxycholic acid shown to be effective prophylactically in meta-analysis of RCTs"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-5 row-odd"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"dc428f",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Gastric or marginal ulceration"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"96d831",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Often associated with NSAID use"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"05553d",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Avoid NSAIDs and smoking"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"72e1b9",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Endoscopy to confirm"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"3eb604",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"PPI therapy"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-6 row-even"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"70024f",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Hypotension, hypoglycemia"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"f743dc",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Improved blood pressure and insulin sensitivity with weight loss"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"d976cb",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Adjust medications as indicated; consider proactive reduction in dose (especially antidiabetic medications)"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-7 row-odd"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"dd07a3",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Gastric outlet obstruction"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"fcf98a",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Sleeve gastrectomy can be complicated by stenosis"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"89595a",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Presents with dysphagia or vomiting"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"1e64b1",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Upper GI series to confirm"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"8aafac",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"May require endoscopic dilation or surgical revision"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-8 row-even"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"5636d4",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Chronic abdominal pain/nausea"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"4bdba3",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Various, including nonadherence to diet recommendations, device slippage (gastric band procedures), bowel obstruction"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"7bf9b2",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Evaluate with endoscopy or CT"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"2a3189",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Re-educate patient on diet modifications if no other cause is identified"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"dbc85e",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Consider low-dose antidepressant therapy"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-9 row-odd"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"747a8a",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Gastroesophageal reflux"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"abede5",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Incidence usually decreases after diversion procedures but may increase after sleeve gastrectomy"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"4d907e",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Evaluate with endoscopy"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"35b0fd",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"PPI therapy, lifestyle modification"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-10 row-even"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"75cde5",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Depression"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"ac800f",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"May be present preoperatively or develop postoperatively"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"3a4f8b",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Monitor for signs of depression and treat with multimodal approach"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"2e9173",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"SSRIs may be less effective post bariatric surgery due to reduced bioavailability"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-11 row-odd"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"18417b",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Regain of weight lost"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"dcab97",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Disordered eating, excess intake of high-calorie liquid/semisolid foods or supplements"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"b6901c",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Re-educate patient on diet modifications"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"ea868a",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Refer to psychiatric care or counseling if indicated"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
}
]
}
]
},
"footnotes":[
[
"GI = gastrointestinal; PPI = proton pump inhibitor; RCT = randomized controlled trial; SSRI = selective serotonin reuptake inhibitor."
]
]
}